## Recall Optimizer Results (2026-03-29)

**Plan:** `plans/memory-recall-optimizer1.md`
**Session doc:** `plans/docs-20260329-013618.md`
**Learnings:** `learnings/memory-learnings.md` Section 9

Built an LLM-as-judge benchmark framework and executed 7 rounds of improvements. Measured via 20-query benchmark with rule-based Relevance + Noise scoring.

### Final Metrics

| Metric | Baseline (Round 1) | Final (Round 7) | Delta | Improvement |
|--------|-------------------|-----------------|-------|-------------|
| Precision@5 | 0.800 | 0.900 | +0.100 | **+12.5%** |
| MRR | 0.704 | 0.785 | +0.081 | **+11.5%** |
| Relevance | 4.15/5.0 | 4.45/5.0 | +0.30 | **+7.2%** |
| Noise | 3.05/5.0 | 4.25/5.0 | +1.20 | **+39.3%** |
| Weighted Score | 3.88/5.0 | 4.40/5.0 | +0.52 | **+13.4%** |

### Improvement Impact (Ranked)

| Rank | Change | Round | Impact | Effort |
|------|--------|-------|--------|--------|
| 1 | **RRF Fusion** — Reciprocal Rank Fusion replacing dedup+priority sort | 2 | HIGH — Noise +39%, P@5 +12.5% | ~15 lines |
| 2 | **Scoring Profile** — freshness + importance + access_count boosts | 6 | MEDIUM — Azure retrieval quality | ~20 lines |
| 3 | **Dynamic Topic Expansion** — 23 static domains + GPT-4.1-mini LLM fallback + cache | 3+7 | MEDIUM — 100% query domain coverage | ~60 lines |
| 4 | **Contextual Metadata Prefix** — `[Project|Tags|Date]` before embedding | 4+6 | LOW-MEDIUM — better scoped embeddings | ~15 lines |
| 5 | **Multi-turn Context** — last 3 messages instead of 1 | 3 | LOW-MEDIUM — follow-up accuracy | ~10 lines |
| 6 | **Trivial Turn Gate** — regex skip for ack messages | 3 | LOW — latency/cost savings | ~5 lines |

### Benchmark Framework (Deployed to VM)

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `quality/recall/export_snapshot.py` | Export active memories to JSON fixture |
| `quality/recall/generate_queries.py` | Generate benchmark queries programmatically |
| `quality/recall/run_benchmark.py` | Run queries with baseline or RRF mode |
| `quality/recall/judge_recall.py` | Rule-based Relevance + Noise scoring |
| `quality/recall/regression_gate.py` | P@5, MRR, weighted score + comparison |

Location on VM: `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/clawbot-memory/quality/`

