  #2 LLM expansion persistent cache    [20 lines, 20 min]
  #3 Tag definition injection (Phase 0) [4 edits, 30 min]

NEXT MONTH:
  #4 Weekly LLM dedup sweep            [new script + cron]
  #5 Importance re-scoring cron         [new script + cron]

NEXT QUARTER:
  #6 Missed-fact analysis              [new script]
  #7 Semantic reranking upgrade        [if hitting 1K cap]

6-MONTH:
  #8 ProMem iterative extraction       [if quality drops below 3.5]
  #9 Claude Code target                [after ClawBot fully validated]
  #10 Full 80q benchmark               [if regression or diagnostic needed]
```

