## Open Questions

1. **Should the monthly health report auto-trigger a re-tagging pass if tag quality drops below threshold?** (Fully autonomous loop vs human-in-the-loop)
2. **Should `access_count` feed back into the scoring profile?** (Frequently-recalled memories rank even higher)
3. **Should we build a web dashboard for memory health?** (Probably overkill — markdown reports are fine for now)
4. **Claude Code session JSONL files ARE accessible on Mac** — should we enable missed-fact analysis for Claude Code too? (Noted in Phase B tuning considerations)
5. **ProMem iterative extraction** — research showed 73.8% recall vs 41% one-shot. Worth the 3-5x cost increase? (Design decision DD-003 flagged)
